<br>
best to find one with the skull staff in his hands.<br>
<br>
<br>
somebody here compared him to lucan?  lucan wouldn't last a minute against the pod, and you'd barely see a dent in the pod's health.<br>
<br>
he is doable by a small high lvl group - going head to head i mean, not kiting and basically having necro or mage exploit the fact that he doesn't attack the pet.<br>
<br>
to give you an idea of how tough he is, he is as tough as a guildmaster <br>
<br>
i once saw a low lvl druid who knew how to get the monk guildmaster in qeynos to fight the pod, that was an impressive fight.<br>
<br>
the pod would beat the monk guildmaster if he was quadding, he'd lose if he was using a 2hblunt. <p><P>Torc<BR>
